(16, 'NEMBO GORE-TEX GLOVES+GORE GRIP TECHNOLOGY', 4, 9, 11, '<p>Unparalleled comfort and protection for motorbike adventures in the most adverse conditions. The Nembo gloves are the top of the Dainese range for touring. The innovative GORE-TEX&reg; Grip technology, which allows complete welding of each layer of the glove to prevent micro-movements of the fabric, provides complete weather protection and a secure grip on the handlebars whenever you ride. The Ergo-Techno knuckles, reinforcements, leather, and TPU combine the highest Dainese protection standards with exceptional comfort so that you can safely live up to your full potential on endless travels filled with motorbike passion.</p>', '<div class=\"tabs-informations\">\r\n<div class=\"product-info\" style=\"border-top: 1px solid #e0dcdc;\">\r\n<div class=\"title-info\">\r\n<h3>CHARACTERISTICS</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"information-product\">\r\n<div class=\"row missing-icon\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-2 col-xs-3 active vertical-aligned\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9 vertical-aligned\">\r\n<p>Dainese Smart Touch</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row missing-icon\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-2 col-xs-3 active vertical-aligned\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9 vertical-aligned\">\r\n<p>Dainese Visor Wiper on the left thumb</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row missing-icon\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-2 col-xs-3 active vertical-aligned\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9 vertical-aligned\">\r\n<p>Reflective inserts</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row missing-icon\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-2 col-xs-3 active vertical-aligned\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-10 col-xs-9 vertical-aligned\">\r\n<p>Soft inserts</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"product-info\">\r\n<div class=\"title-info\">\r\n<h3>ERGONOMICS</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"information-product\">\r\n<div class=\"row missing-icon\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-2 col