(18, 'AGV Sport Mojave Jacket', 2, 5, 4, '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: #151211; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px;\">AGV Sport Mojave Jacket</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">The Mojave Jacket from AGV Sport is adventure-ready. With an emphasis on airflow, the Mojave Jacket features large mesh panels at the chest and back designed with the hard-working ADV rider in mind. Magnetic fasteners at the chest vents and a collar-stay for even more airflow maximize cooling. Water-resistant zippers at the same vents and a waterproof thermal liner team-up to keep unwanted nature out. Smoothways impact armor at the elbows and shoulders and a back protector all are included.&nbsp; A circumferential zipper allows the jacket to mate to the Mojave Pants - creating a full ADV riding suit that meets CE garment certifications.&nbsp;</p>', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: #151211; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px;\">Features:&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; list-style-position: outside; font-size: 16px; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Abrasion resistant polyester main construction&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Reinforced impact areas at elbows and shoulders</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Water resistant 75g removable thermal liner</li>\r\n<li 