(19, 'AGV Sport Palomar Jacket', 2, 4, 4, '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: #151211; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px;\">AGV Sport Palomar Jacket</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">Sharing its name with the mountainous Palomar Loop in San Diego County, the Palomar Jacket from AGV Sport exhilarates the soul like your favorite series of apexes. Distressed cowhide construction is rugged with a livery of leather stripes as a shout to racers of yore. Contrasting panels at the chest, shoulders, inner arms and back are perforated for hot-weather ventilation. Add the removable 75 gram thermal liner, and the Palomar will serve you just as handily on those cool midnight runs. Burnished fasteners, pleated elbows and stitched AGV Sport branding complete the look. Smoothways CE Level 2 armor - included for the elbows, shoulders and back - are a nod to the today\'s racer and contemporary safety engineering.&nbsp;</p>', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: #151211; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px;\">Features:&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; list-style-position: outside; font-size: 16px; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Vintage cowhide construction</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Perforated panels at the chest, shoulders, inner arms and back</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Removable 75g thermal liner</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Embroidered AGV Sport branding</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Drop seat with hook and loop waist adjusters</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Inside pocket</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Jacket to pants connection loop</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Advanced Safety Stitching Construction (ASSC) with mil-spec thread and triple stitching at impact zones</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Smoothways CE Level 2 elbow, shoulder and back protection</li>\r\n</ul>', 'agv', 1),
(20, 'STELLA ANDES V3 DRYSTAR® JACKET', 2, 6, 7, '<p><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\">The Andes v3 Jacket is anatomically engineered for an optimized women&rsquo;s fit and its exclusive Alpinestars Drystar</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; background-color: #f8f8f8;\">&reg;</span><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\">&nbsp;construction ensures 100% waterproofing and high levels of breathability, even in difficult riding conditions. The technically advanced construction of this jacket offers protection and abrasion resistance and is adaptable to all weather conditions.</span></p>', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\">&bull; Front waterproof cargo pockets for convenience and peace-of-mind closure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\" />&bull; Large, external utility pocket on lower back, plus internal pockets and a waterproof wallet pocket for real-world practicality.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\" />&bull; Integrated soft edge collar and 3D mesh construction for enhanced comfort over long distances.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\" />&bull; Premium YKK zipper for main front closure offers adaptable, secure and convenient closure.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\" />&bull; Adjustable bottom side gussets for an optimal fit.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\" />&bull; Removable long-sleeve thermal liner (100g body 80g sleeves) ensures comfort on hot or cold days.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\" />&bull; Pre-contoured sleeves with stretch panels on elbows for comfort and freedom of movement</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #111111; font-family: Helvetica, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Lucida Grande\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f8f8f8;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\" />&bull; Hook and loop-closing waist adjustment belt ensures a highly customizable fit</p>', 'alphine', 1),
(21, 'Arai Ram-X Helmet (LG)', 1, 2, 8, '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: #151211; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px;\">Arai Ram-X Helmet</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">With the Ram-X, Arai takes a leap forward from their previous premium open-face touring helmet, the XC. The Ram-X features the newly designed VAS-Z shield system with a lower pivot point providing smooth actuation and improved safety. In a nod to touring riders, the Ram-X includes a Pro Shade System out of the box which provides the convenience of a drop down sun visor without compromising the shell and thus safety of the helmet. Taking design clues and the ventilation scheme from Arai\'s race helmet, the Corsair X, the Ram-X offer best-in-class ventilation for a comfortable ride no matter what.</p>', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: #151211; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px;\">Features:</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; list-style-position: outside; font-size: 16px; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Super Fiber Laminate shell with new Z-compound</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Corsair X ventilation scheme</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Multiple-foam interiors for comfort</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Removable/replaceable cheek pads for custom fit</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Side cowl exhausts</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">VAS-Z Pro Shade shield, holder and base plates</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Advance flip up face shield&nbsp;precurved and super scratch-resistant</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Meets or exceeds Snell 2015 and DOT standards</li>\r\n</ul>', 'arai', 1);
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `name`, `category`, `subcategory`, `brand`, `description`, `features`, `keywords`, `status`) VALUES
(22, 'Alpinestars Supertech M10 Carbon Helmet', 1, 3, 7, '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: #151211; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px;\">Alpinestars Supertech S-M10 Carbon Helmet</h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">Rome wasn\'t built in a day. Don\'t expect a sprawling city that can be considered the first ever metropolis or the capital of the world to be made lickety split.&nbsp; Similarly, Alpinestars\' first foray into off-road motorcycle helmets took years of development, but the pay-off is a high end carbon fiber helmet with state of the art features and materials.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">The Alpinestars Supertech S-M10 Carbon helmet uses a lightweight carbon fiber shell that comes in 4 different shell sizes. Its visor release system holds the visor/peak securely, but releases in the event of impact. Alpinestars provides 2 peaks with 2 different angles depending on the rider\'s preference. Ventilation is top notch with numerous inlet and outlet ports connected with a series of airways that snake through the interior. The internal liner is an amalgamation of protective and comfort materials. A multiple density inner liner absorbs impacts while a&nbsp;<span class=\"redline-tooltip redline-tooltip--help-keywords\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: inline-block; position: relative; margin-left: 0px;\" data-js=\"Tooltip.Container\"><span class=\"redline-tooltip__help-keyword\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px dotted; cursor: pointer;\" data-js=\"Tooltip.Icon\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-weight: bold;\">MIPS</span></span></span>-E2 liner protects against rotational energy. Alpinestars\' proprietary A-Head system is an adjustable head frame that allows you to adjust how the helmet sits on the head. Soft EPP foam cushions the bottom lip of the helmet to help avoid collarbone injury in the event of a crash. Emergency removable cheek pads along with a design prepared for the E-Ject helmet removal system make the Alpinestars Supertech S-M10 Carbon Helmet a protective motocross helmet filled to the brim with safety features.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0.625em; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">This isn\'t a fast food burger that has been sitting under a heat lamp. This type of refinement has to be made from the ground up. The feature packed Alpinestars Supertech S-M10 Carbon Helmet is a Michelin starred restaurant\'s testing menu compared to lower end helmets.&nbsp;</p>', '<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px 0px 0.5rem; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; color: #151211; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-size: 16px;\">Features:</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: inherit; line-height: 24px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 1.25rem; padding: 0px; list-style-position: outside; font-size: 16px; color: #151211; font-family: ProximaNova, Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Lightweight outer shell constructed from carbon fiber</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Four shell sizes</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Multiple density inner liner</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Fitted with E-2 MIPS</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Easy release peak</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">2 peaks included, one regular and one super high</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">A-Head adjustable top pad height</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Maximum ventilation with 19 intake and 5 exhaust ports</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Side shell shape coupled with soft EPP foam to prevent damage to collarbone in case of crash</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Removable, emergency release cheek pads with 3D contoured foam</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Removable anti-bacterial and hydrophobic comfort liner</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">Hydration prepared</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">E-Ject prepared</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: inherit;\">DOT and ECE approved</li>\r\n</ul>', 'alphine', 1),
(24, 'MT Blade 2SV Trick Blue Helmet', 1, 1, 3, '<p><span style=\"color: #777777; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">This one&rsquo;s an outcome of sheer transformation. An all-purpose helmet that is not just out of the ordinary, but is destined to change from good to great. The Trick makes you feel like a superhero on the inside. After all, confidence is in the head.</span></p>', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; min-height: 1px; color: #777777;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Shell:</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #777777;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">High Impact Injected polycarbonate shell for improved protection.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Multiple Shell Sizes - to provide the right fit for maximum safety.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Multi-density inner EPS, designed for better impact absorption.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Unique Aerodynamic Shell, with an integrated split-wing spoiler ( First in the Industry) &nbsp;</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Multi-ventilation system with optimized airflow to help the rider feel comfy during extreme heat.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; min-height: 1px; color: #777777;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Visor:</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 15px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: #777777;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pin-lock ready Max Vision Visor - equipped to attach/detach Anti-fog inserts. For a clear edge-to-edge vision even in foggy weather conditions.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Adjustable Internal Sun Visor for cozy long-distance riding in the blistering sun.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Turbulators along the sides of the visor to reduce buffeting.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Push-to-release locking mechanism for easy opening and closing of the visor.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">MT&rsquo;s Quick Release System (QRS) helps in removing and replacing the visor effortlessly.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; vertical-align: baseline; min-height: 1px; color: #777777;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: 